        "title": "Add Anthropic Sandbox Runtime provider",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add Anthropic Sandbox Runtime as canonical `anthropic-sandbox-runtime` with alias `srt`\n- keep v1 as a local one-shot delegated-run provider with no persistent lease semantics\n- wire Anthropic-specific config, env overrides, docs, tests, and live sandbox enforcement smoke coverage\n\nRefs: https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/267\n\n## Verification\n- `go test -race ./...`\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `node --test scripts/*.test.js`\n- `scripts/check-docs.sh`\n- `go build -trimpath -o bin/crabbox ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `bin/crabbox providers --json` reports only canonical `anthropic-sandbox-runtime` with alias `srt`\n- generic `sandbox-runtime` is rejected as unknown\n- official `@anthropic-ai/sandbox-runtime@0.0.54` live smoke passed: doctor, one-shot run, allowed write/read, denied secret read, and denied network\n- `autoreview --mode local` clean\n- fresh GitHub CI and Socket checks green\n",
